      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 00:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受 BOT 政策和政治风险影响，全球对泰国债务的追捧或将降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/global-rush-for-thai-debt-may-cool-on-bot-policy-political-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于泰国与其他国家相比货币政策更为紧缩，且政治风险上升，导致泰国主权债券的吸引力降低，外国投资者可能开始避开泰国主权债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/global-rush-for-thai-debt-may-cool-on-bot-policy-political-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 00:02:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
